e infrastructure is very  comfortable and located at nice place.\\nI\'m a front-end developer here and learning very well.\\nThanks for excellent guidance and knowledge.\",\"time\":1595246477,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"Shadan Salah\",\"author_url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.google.com\\/maps\\/contrib\\/106184961787396163930\\/reviews\",\"language\":\"en\",\"original_language\":\"en\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https:\\/\\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\\/a\\/ACg8ocJ0E3OAQ1NGmy5q7InTKg2SdkdOHflCLYvVwFoQAjN3eu82gw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo\",\"rating\":4,\"relative_time_description\":\"a year ago\",\"text\":\"Highly skilled team of professionals. Would love to work with them again!\",\"time\":1683809901,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"Krishna Vishwakarma\",\"author_url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.google.com\\/maps\\/contrib\\/117819928554972850125\\/reviews\",\"language\":\"en-US\",\"original_language\":\"sv\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https:\\/\\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\\/a-\\/ALV-UjX3IXKRNjf0s4GOf9sffjgGjnWqhUwjIndhm-w-ej_q8unTff1S=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo\",\"rating\":5,\"relative_time_description\":\"a year ago\",\"text\":\"Exile\",\"time\":1658313831,\"translated\":true}]', '1', '1', '2024-06-03 14:25:38', '2024-06-03 14:25:38', NULL);
